stereotypes. <strong>Casey Affleck</strong> won best actor for <em>Manchest=
er by the Sea</em> in 2017 despite all the noise around his settlement of a=
 sexual harassment lawsuit. <em>Jojo Rabbit </em>was pilloried by the Very =
Online Left=E2=80=94until it scored six Oscar nominations and won best adap=
ted screenplay.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p st=
yle=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">That stuff has never really mattered to=
 the Academy when they like a movie. And it certainly doesn=E2=80=99t
matter now that Twitter has imploded and social media has been delegitimize=
d as a swamp of misinformation and dance videos. In fact, the most importan=
