argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Disney gave the MCU a sabbatical in 2024, slati=
ng just one surefire
smash=E2=80=94<em>Deadpool &amp; Wolverine</em>=E2=80=94for the entire year=
=2E Part of that film=E2=80=99s success ca=
n be attributed to the fact that it=
 featured established franchise characters, beloved even among those unaffl=
icted by a slavish devotion to the MCU. Marvel won=E2=80=99t have that same=
 assurance this year. After all, <em>Captain America: Brave New World</em>,=
<em> Thunderbolts</em>, and <em>The Fantastic Four: First Steps </em>featur=
e new, or at least less established, characters. Still, Disney is hoping th=
at
